    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage including multiple deep scratches, dents, and paint deterioration in several areas. The interior is heavily worn with notable damage to the upholstery, trim, and other surfaces. Mechanical issues are present and will require attention. Sold as-is.",
